toGraph

public Graph toGraph(java.lang.String... _pkCol)
convert table to graph. subjects are the given pk cols appended with / seperators. predicates are the table column headers. Objects are the other column values. Thus we have rows * #(non pk cols) triples

Parameters:
_pkCol - primary key column names

result graph
